{"tid":2122624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近排時事台既風氣真係好差","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:35:34.000Z","uid":61105,"like":48,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac068a990c16d2541d4cf240dd3505a92ee455e","tid":2122624,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"其實我懷疑呢度PR五毛已經佔左大多數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動策略post，正經高質討論愈來愈少，最多就係嘈下公務員/xx機構員工值唔值得批鬥、貼舊聞/大紀元級數既傳聞圍爐打飛機、恥笑藍絲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n上面既野有咩共通點？就係大家嘈完/自high完之後對現實係完全無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實呢個世界好大，好多野更加值得大家關心。同埋以前大家講到口臭，見到罵戰post用不推文/負皮上一頁、fc精神已經無晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知實會有人話我覆咩post係我自由，我想講再係咁落去玩爛左個討論區，個惡果都係大家承受番，你睇我個user name就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我識好多做實事既人已經好耐無上連登，但我對呢度仲有希望，好想個氣氛番番舊年個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫幫手，見到無價值既post（fc左既振奮post另計）盡量唔好覆，由佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"b1be5d0c1eddf366313cdc16cbdd12bd3cd115f6","tid":2122624,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f530dc95e62a2c2e16069bff5814d436a4cb916","tid":2122624,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd9094a4262e3934073fe9e4ed8b293419f6db5","tid":2122624,"uid":113155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"係，有時睇啲成版topic，內容唔同，但格式好似，以前唔會咁。"},{"pid":"16945b5ca7405102b2518a96404842106cdd0ea2","tid":2122624,"uid":150483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202